WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.216
My name is Lovegrove.

00:00:01.240 --> 00:00:05.336
I only know nine Lovegroves,
two of which are my parents.

00:00:05.360 --> 00:00:09.176
They are first cousins, and you know
what happens when, you know --

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:10.416
(Laughter)

00:00:10.440 --> 00:00:14.656
So there's a terribly weird
freaky side to me,

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:16.536
which I'm fighting with all the time.

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:19.336
So to try and get through today,

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:22.416
I've kind of disciplined myself
with an 18-minute talk.

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:23.936
I was hanging on to have a pee.

00:00:23.960 --> 00:00:26.296
I thought perhaps
if I was hanging on long enough,

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:28.320
that would guide me
through the 18 minutes.

00:00:28.344 --> 00:00:30.656
(Laughter)